    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a protocol for efficiently routing to multicast groups that may span wide-area (and inter-domain) internets.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.  Discussion and suggestions for improvement are requested.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
